geomentry of this device is simplified into a simple linear\n sequence of blocks.\n\n Port usage (base +)\n 0 - Command\n 1 - Status\n 2 - Value MSB\n 3 - Value\n 4 - Value\n 5 - Value LSB\n\n Commands are:\n 0 - Do nothing\n 1 - Set drive\n 2 - Set starting block\n 3 - Set block count\n 4 - Set DMA address\n 5 - Read data\n 6 - Write data\n 7 - Read max drive number\n 8 - Read max block number\n Status bits are\n 7 - Unused\n 6 - Unused\n 5 - Unused\n 4 - Bad command\n 3 - Drive out of range\n 2 - Count out of range\n 1 - Starting block out of range\n 0 - Drive out of range\n\n In operation, write the value first and then issue the set command to\n set a value.  To read a value, issue a read command, then read the value.","parameters":[{"name":"self","description":""}]}},{"id":"c614c7b3e34f1d76","name":"max_drive","qualified_name":"BBS.Sim_CPU.io.disk.floppy.max_drive","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"../../../../home/runner/.local/share/alire/builds/bbs_simcpu_0.5.0_c779a728/9cdc441e7ff3f33fced7ac7acaa0da633fb83bcec604d59dd89b3ca09151f539/src/io/bbs-sim_cpu-io-disk-floppy.ads","line":218,"column":13},"code":"function max_drive(self : in out hd_ctrl) return byte","documentation":{"description":"=========================================================================","parameters":[{"name":"self","description":""}]}},{"id":"cbfa831112332f25","name":"name","qualified_name":"BBS.Sim_CPU.io.disk.floppy.name","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"../../../../home/runner/.local/share/alire/builds/bbs_simcpu_0.5.0_c779a728/9cdc441e7ff3f33fced7ac7acaa0da633fb83bcec604d59dd89b3ca09151f539/src/io/bbs-sim_cpu-io-disk-floppy.ads","line":75,"column":13},"code":"function name(self : in out fd_ctrl) return string","documentation":{"description":"\n  Set which exception to use","parameters":[{"name":"self","description":""}]}},{"id":"72e75e766495a5a4","name":"name","qualified_name":"BBS.Sim_CPU.io.disk.floppy.name","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"../../../.